\c 11
\s Rusvingo rweBhabheri
\p
\v 1 Zvino nyika yose yaiva yerurimi rwumwe neyeshoko rimwe.
\v 2 Zvino zvakaitika vachifamba kubva kumabvazuva, kuti vakawana bani munyika yeShinari, ndokugarako.
\v 3 Ndokuti umwe neumwe kumuvakidzani wake: Uyai, ngatiite zvidhina, tizvipise zvikuru. Zvino zvidhina zvakava mabwe kwavari, netara ikava dope kwavari.
\v 4 Zvino vakati: Uyai, ngatizvivakire guta neshongwe ine musoro urikudenga, uye ngatizviitirei zita, zvikasadaro tingapararira pamusoro pechiso chenyika yose.
\p
\v 5 Zvino Jehovha wakaburuka kuzoona guta neshongwe, yakangi yavakwa nevanakomana vevanhu.
\v 6 Jehovha ndokuti: Tarira, rudzi nderwumwe, uye vane rurimi rwumwe vose, zvino ndizvo zvavanotanga kuita; uye ikozvino hakuchina chinhu chavangada kuita chavangadziviswa.
\v 7 Uyai, ngatiburuke, tivhiringidze rurimi rwavo ipapo, kuti vasanzwa mutauro weumwe neumwe.
\v 8 Naizvozvo Jehovha wakavaparadzira kubva ipapo pamusoro pechiso chenyika, vakamira kuvaka guta.
\v 9 Naizvozvo vakatumidza zita raro kuti Bhabheri, nekuti ipapo Jehovha wakavhiringidza rurimi rwenyika yose; uye kubva ipapo Jehovha akavaparadzira pachiso chenyika yose.
\s Vanakomana vaShemu
\p
\v 10 Awa marudzi aShemu. Shemu wakange ane makore zana, akabereka Aripakishadhi, makore maviri shure kwemafashame.
\v 11 Shemu ndokurarama, shure kwekubereka Aripakishadhi, makore mazana mashanu; akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 12 Aripakishadhi ndokurarama makore makumi matatu nemashanu, akabereka Shera.
\v 13 Aripakishadhi ndokurarama, shure kwekubereka kwake Shera, makore mazana mana nematatu; akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 14 Shera ndokurarama makore makumi matatu, akabereka Ebheru.
\v 15 Shera ndokurarama, shure kwekubereka kwake Ebheru, makore mazana mana nematatu; akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 16 Ebheru ndokurarama makore makumi matatu nemana, akabereka Peregi.
\v 17 Ebheru ndokurarama, shure kwekubereka kwake Peregi, makore mazana mana nemakumi matatu; akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 18 Peregi ndokurarama makore makumi matatu, akabereka Rehu.
\v 19 Zvino Peregi wakararama, shure kwekubereka kwake Rehu, makore mazana maviri nemapfumbamwe; akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 20 Rehu ndokurarama makore makumi matatu nemaviri, akabereka Serugu.
\v 21 Zvino Rehu wakararama, shure kwekubereka kwake Serugu, makore mazana maviri nemanomwe; akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 22 Serugu ndokurarama makore makumi matatu, akabereka Nahori.
\v 23 Zvino Serugu wakararama, shure kwekubereka kwake Nahori, makore mazana maviri, akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 24 Nahori ndokurarama makore makumi maviri nemapfumbamwe, akabereka Tera.
\v 25 Zvino Nahori wakararama, shure kwekubereka kwake Tera, makore zana negumi nemapfumbamwe, akabereka vanakomana nevanasikana.
\p
\v 26 Tera ndokurarama makore makumi manomwe, akabereka Abhuramu, Nahori naHarani.
\p
\v 27 Zvino izvi zvizvarwa zvaTera. Tera wakabereka Abhuramu, Nahori naHarani; Harani ndokubereka Roti;
\v 28 Harani akafa, baba vake Tera \add vasati\add* vafa, panyika yechiberekerwa chake, muUri yevaKaradhea.
\v 29 Zvino Abhuramu naNahori vakazvitorera vakadzi; zita remukadzi waAbhuramu \add raiva\add* Sarai; uye zita remukadzi waNahori \add raiva\add* Mirika, mukunda waHarani, baba vaMirika, nababa vaIsika.
\v 30 Asi Sarai waiva mhanje, wakange asina mwana.
\v 31 Zvino Tera wakatora Abhuramu mwanakomana wake, naRoti, mwanakomana waHarani, mwanakomana wemwanakomana wake, naSarai, muroora wake, mukadzi waAbhuramu mwanakomana wake; vakabva Uri yevaKaradhea navo, kuenda kunyika yeKenani; vakasvika Harani, vakagarapo.
\v 32 Zvino mazuva aTera aiva makore mazana maviri nemashanu; Tera akafira Harani.
